quran[6]{c,v,t}:
  16,84,Aur jiss din hum her ummat mein say gawah khara keren gay phir kafiron ko na ijazat di jaye gi aur na unn say toba kerney ko kaha jayega
  16,85,Aur jab yeh zalim azab dekh len gay phir na to unn say halka kiya jayega aur na woh dheel diye jayen gay
  16,86,Aur jab mushrikeen apney sharikon ko dekh len gay to kahen gay aey humaray perwerdigar! Yehi humaray woh shareek hain jinhen hum tujhay chor ker pukara kertay thay pus woh unhen jawab den gay kay tum bilkul hi jhootay ho
  16,87,Uss din woh sab (aajiz ho ker) Allah kay samney ita’at ka iqrar paish keren gay aur jo bohtan bazi kiya kertay thay woh sab unn say gumm hojayega
  16,88,Jinhon ney kufur kiya aur Allah ki raah say roka hum unhen azab per azab barhatay jayen gay yeh badla hoga unn ki fitna pardaziyon ka
  16,89,Aur jiss din hum her ummat mein unhi mein say unn kay muqablay mein gawah khara keren gay aur tujhay inn sab per gawah bana ker layen gay aur hum ney tujh per yeh kitab nazil farmaee hai jiss mein her cheez ka shafi biyan hai aur hidayat aur rehmat aur khuskhabri say musalmanon kay liye